title: Russia to expel UK diplomats as crisis over nerve toxin attack deepens
text:
Russia to expel UK diplomats as crisis over nerve toxin attack deepens Friday, March 16, 2018 - 01:09 
Russia is set to expel British diplomats in retaliation for Prime Minister Theresa May's decision to kick out 23 Russians over an attack with military-grade nerve agent on English soil. Julian Satterthwaite reports
